{"tid":810461,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"魏韵芝真係全TVB最屈機藝人","createTime":"2018-09-08T04:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T12:08:20.000Z","uid":1426,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0383ed4095a93ab4da255b845567b6f598ae780b","tid":810461,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/bka.mpweekly.com/focus/local/名人專線/20180827-128693/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fbka.mpweekly.com%2Ffocus%2Flocal%2F%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%88%E7%B7%9A%2F20180827-128693%2Famp&d=9xv0JFbQRmkqdytgjbZEH7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2e4cbe79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/bka.mpweekly.com/focus/local/名人專線/20180827-128693/amp</a><br />\nPCLL,痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人生不止為賺錢<br />\nJoyce在TVB工作了兩年，主要是做主持，至於擁有律師牌的她表示一直有續牌，有考慮過再掛牌，不過她做事務律師以辦公室工作為主，不是她想過的人生，所以想在TVB再闖一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係王國旌外孫，有樣有身材（小肥）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTl4kg7ZQ7Cm8typeVqHlh0f_12GF0JTZbQ4